{"tid":2264856,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"親友向罪名不成立的被告表示「你聽日可以準時返工啦」，對方回答「係呀，可以返工啦」","createTime":"2020-10-31T03:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T04:09:26.000Z","uid":378282,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33af2e69bb0295fc499496b5a0b0da11dbb0a9a9","tid":2264856,"uid":378282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"「陣地社工」成員陳虹秀等8人，被控去年 8 月 31 日在灣仔參與暴動案，法官沈小民早前裁定陳虹秀的暴動罪表證不成立，當庭獲釋，餘下7名被告則繼續處理，並於今日裁決，法官裁定7人暴動罪不成立，第四被告另被控的一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器亦不成立。<br />\n<br />\n法官宣佈各被告罪名不成立一刻，庭內隨即掌聲雷動。散庭後有被告難掩激動，失聲痛哭，有被告與親友及律師相擁致謝，眾人均眼泛淚光，場面感人，期間有人指「呢個先係正常結果」，亦有人指「好似突然派彩咁」，更有親友向罪名不成立的被告表示，「你聽日可以準時返工啦」，對方回答「係呀，可以返工啦」，如釋重負。<br />\n<br />\n【相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HPNseC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HPNseC&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdtC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=694987f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HPNseC</a> 】"},{"pid":"e95dcb252dc8aade2286d07ced5686f748d0f912","tid":2264856,"uid":378282,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdJe8TG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdJe8TG.jpg&h=2cc687cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時真係好諷刺 咁大件事 第一件事竟然係諗番工"},{"pid":"e3fc7e8d4c6692987f4cf4d7051e155b70b75fbd","tid":2264856,"uid":378282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iW05v7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiW05v7v.jpg&h=95e0e411&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f28656051ef2fb95c51188d2c3701915dde05f3d","tid":2264856,"uid":378282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/